        {
            "text": "The first-step fit determines p 1 and p 2 by fixing Re (\u03bb) and Im (\u03bb) in the products Re (z)Re (\u03bb), Im (z)Im (\u03bb), Im (z)[Re (\u03bb)] 2 , and Re (z)Re (\u03bb)Im (\u03bb). ",
