            "text": "After fixing these terms, the relation between the vectors y and p is strictly linear,",
            "section": "III. FIT RESULTS",
            "paragraph_rank": 28,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "where M 1 uses Im (\u03bb) = 0.67 and Re (\u03bb) = \u22120.74, motivated by the results of analyses assuming CP T symmetry [7]. ",
            "section": "III. FIT RESULTS",
            "paragraph_rank": 29,
