            "section": "III. FIT RESULTS",
            "paragraph_rank": 33,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "This first-step fit yields p 1 = 0.001 \u00b1 0.023 \u00b1 0.017 , p 2 = 0.689 \u00b1 0.030 \u00b1 0.015 . ",
            "section": "III. FIT RESULTS",
            "paragraph_rank": 34,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "(18) ",
