        {
            "text": "Eqs. ",
            "section": "III. FIT RESULTS",
            "paragraph_rank": 36,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "(12) to (17) are then applied again, replacing M 1 with the new relations matrix M 2 . ",
