        {
            "text": "The Re (z) result deviates from zero by 2.1 \u03c3. ",
            "section": "III. FIT RESULTS",
            "paragraph_rank": 38,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "The result for |\u03bb| can be easily converted into |A/A| by using the world average of measurements for |q/p|. ",
            "section": "III. FIT RESULTS",
            "paragraph_rank": 38,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "With |q/p| = 1.0008 \u00b1 0.0008 [7], we obtain |A/A| = 0.999 \u00b1 0.023 \u00b1 0.017 ,",
            "section": "III. FIT RESULTS",
