            "text": "in agreement with CP T symmetry. ",
            "section": "III. FIT RESULTS",
            "paragraph_rank": 39,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "Using the matrix algebra in Eqs. ",
            "section": "III. FIT RESULTS",
            "paragraph_rank": 39,
            "section_rank": 4
